<topic id="open-find-resource-view">
  <title>Open/Find Resource View</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Searching documents<indexterm>Open/Find Resource view</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>Open/Find Resource view</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_eyt_bgk_54b">The <uicontrol>Open/Find Resource</uicontrol> view is designed to offer advanced search
      capabilities either by using a simple text search or by using the <xref
        href="http://lucene.apache.org/core/old_versioned_docs/versions/2_9_1/queryparsersyntax.html"
        format="html" scope="external">Apache Lucene - Query Parser Syntax</xref>. By default, the
      view is presented in the left side of the <ph keyref="product"/> layout, next to the <xref
        href="using-the-project-view.dita#using-the-project-view"><uicontrol>Project</uicontrol>
        view</xref>
      <ph product="author editor">or <xref href="dita-maps-manager.dita#dita-maps-manager"
            ><uicontrol>DITA Maps Manager</uicontrol></xref></ph>. <ph
        conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view"/></p>
    <p id="p_fyt_bgk_54b">
      <fig id="fig_gyt_bgk_54b">
        <title>Open/Find Resource View</title>
        <image href="../img/find-resource-view.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p id="p_hyt_bgk_54b">You can use this view to find a file in the current <ph keyref="product"/>
      project <ph product="editor author">or in one of the <xref keyref="glossentry_ditamap"
            ><term>DITA maps</term></xref> opened in <xref keyref="dita_edit-maps" format="dita">the
            <uicontrol>DITA Maps Manager</uicontrol> view</xref>
      </ph> by typing only a few letters of the file name of a document or a fragment of the content
      you are searching for. The <uicontrol>Open/Find Resource</uicontrol> view also supports
      searching in document edits (comments, tracked change insertions/deletions, and highlighted
      content) by selecting the <xref href="#open-find-resource-view/in-reviews" format="dita"
          ><uicontrol>In reviews</uicontrol> option</xref>.</p>
    <section conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/search-results-section" id="d2e56"/>
    <section id="options_available_in_the_view">
      <title>Options Available in the View</title>
      <p id="p_jyt_bgk_54b">The <uicontrol>Open/Find Resource</uicontrol> view offers the following options:<ul id="ul_kyt_bgk_54b">
          <li id="li_lyt_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol><image href="../img/Settings16.png"/>Settings</uicontrol> - Drop-down menu
            that includes the following settings for the view:<ul id="ul_myt_bgk_54b">
              <li id="li_nyt_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/clear-index"/></li>
              <li id="li_oyt_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>Show description</uicontrol> - Presents the search results in a more
                compact form, displaying only the title and the location of the resources.</li>
              <li id="li_pyt_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/options"
                  product="author developer editor json"/></li>
            </ul></li>
          <li id="li_qyt_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/in-file-paths"
              product="author developer editor json"/></li>
          <li id="li_ryt_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/in-content"
              product="author developer editor json"/></li>
          <li id="in-reviews" irina="irina"><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/in-reviews"
              product="author developer editor json"/></li>
          <li id="li_syt_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/reindex"/></li>
        </ul></p>
    </section>
    <section id="contextual_menu_actions">
