    <p id="p_uyt_bgk_54b">
      <note id="note3">You can drag a resource from the <uicontrol>Open/Find Resource</uicontrol>
        view and drop it in a DocBook, DITA, TEI or XHTML document to create a link to that
        resource.</note>
    </p>
